sellerCard.description:
Hi I am a  wordpress Developer. I have plenty of experience for designing logos, icons, wordpress sites and other graphics.
contact for more details.

I have almost 5 years of experience on different PHP framework and different wordpress theme.

Theme customization, designing website on wordpress and plugin as well.

description.content:
Hii,

If you are facing any issues In your PHP | Laravel | Codeigniter | WordPress or if you want to create a new website then you are in the right place.

As a professional web developer with 3+ years of experience in web development, I can build you a new web app from scratch by using the latest technology. Also, I can work on existing PHP |  Laravel | Codeigniter | WordPress websites for things like 

  1. Install or migrate script on your hosting
  2. Convert your static web app into the dynamic web app
  3. Add new features or improve the current website
  4. Fix bugs from your existing site 
  5. Upgrade to the latest version 
  6. Integrate the application with external API such as Paypal, Stripe 
  7. anything else! (please message me with your issue)


Why choose me?


  • 3+ years of experience as a web Developer
  • 100% Satisfaction 
  • No security risks 
  • Easy to work 
  • Quality Work


IMPORTANT*

Before you order this gig come to a discussion and let me know your exact requirement.
